 Setwerk Films has dropped episode 8 of its web series “Grow Up or Nuts” season 2 and in this episode, the “Lagos Big Girls” are here with an offer for Mudi. This season is packed with more fun, thrilling and exciting moments with your favourite girls. In this season, all mysteries are solved and more truths revealed. This amazing series was shot by Setwerk Films, starring Sophie Alakija-Rammal, Efe Irele, Okawa Shaznay and many others. Produced by Efe Irele and directed by Jide “J Blaze” Oyegbile. Watch the new episode below: 